A to-do app is a tool that helps you organize your tasks and stay on top of your schedule: 
Task management: To-do apps can help you prioritize tasks, set deadlines, and manage your workflow. 
Task organization: Some to-do apps let you organize tasks in different ways, such as lists, boards, or calendars. 
Task reminders: Some to-do apps can send reminders for deadlines. 
Team collaboration: Some to-do apps let teams collaborate on tasks
To-do lists offer a way to increase productivity, stopping you from forgetting things, helps prioritise tasks, manage tasks effectively, use time wisely and improve time management as well as workflow.

